----- stdout -----
An opinionated Markdown note-taking and management CLI.

Usage: ntropy [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  init       Initialize a vault (idempotent)
  new        Create a note from the default template and open it
  search     Browse, filter or full-text search notes
  edit       Open a specific note by id or query
  reconcile  Realign drifted filenames and rebuild views
  delete     Delete a note by id or query
  view       Manage materialized view definitions
  tags       List all tags with note counts
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --vault <PATH>     Operate on the vault at this path (overrides all other resolution)
  -n, --non-interactive  Force non-interactive (plain) behavior even on a TTY
      --strict           Treat malformed/badly-named notes as errors instead of warnings
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version


